OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy skies
OL,6,Freturning into Wednesday evening, with
OL,7,Fareas of mist and fog developing
OL,8,Fthrough the night. Chilly, with an
OL,9,Fisolated frost probable as winds fall
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,13,Ffog soon clearing to coasts with
OL,14,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,15,Fsunny spells and light winds. Mild
OL,16,Finland, but cooler towards the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
